author: Viva La Dirt League
description:
A goblin mob boss, clad in steampunk finery, Naz is the firecracker leader of the Blackcoin. Naz carries his explosive weapons wherever he goes, and sleeps with one eye open.
Welcome Naz Grimracket Into The Darklands. Premieres 25th September on VivaPlus or 2nd October on Youtube.
